<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Reyna Aydhina Maritza — Frontend Developer</title>

    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;800&family=Clash+Display:wght@500;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <!-- NAV -->
    <header class="nav">
      <div class="nav-inner">
        <div class="brand">
          <span class="dot"></span>
          Reyna Aydhina
        </div>

         <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
    </button>

        <nav class="nav-links">
          <a href="#about">About</a>
          <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
          <a href="#portfolio">Portfolio</a>
          <a href="#contact">Contact</a>

          <% if (session && session.isLogin) { %>
          <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-secondary" style="margin-left: 15px"
            >Logout</a
          >
          <% } else { %>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            style="margin-left: 15px"
            onclick="openLoginModal()"
          >
            Login
          </button>
          <% } %>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="wrap">
      <!-- HERO -->
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="bg-name" aria-hidden="true">REYNA AYDHINA</div>
        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div class="left">
            <h1>Reyna Aydhina<br />Maritza</h1>
            <span class="role">Frontend Developer</span>
            <p class="lead">
              Hai! Aku Reyna Aydhina Maritza, seorang developer dengan
              ketertarikan pada frontend dan UI design.
            </p>
            <div class="cta">
              <!-- <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#portfolio"
                ><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i>&nbsp;Lihat Karya</a
              > -->
              <a
                class="btn btn-primary"
                href="/pdf/cv-reyna.pdf"
                target="_blank"
              >
                <i class="fa-solid fa-file-pdf"></i>&nbsp;CV
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="center">
            <img src="/img/rere1.png" alt="Reyna Aydhina" />
          </div>

          <div class="right">
            <div class="card profile-mini">
              <div class="avatar">R</div>
              <div>
                <strong>It’s me, Reyna 🦋</strong><br />
                <small class="muted" style="color: var(--muted)"
                  >I don’t chase bugs, bugs chase me</small
                >
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div
                style="
                  display: flex;
                  align-items: center;
                  justify-content: space-between;
                "
              >
                <strong>My Personality Pack</strong>
              </div>
              <div
                class="rating"
                aria-label="5 emojis about me"
                style="font-size: 1.4rem"
              >
                <span>😠</span>
                <span>🍜</span>
                <span>😭</span>
                <span>🐱</span>
                <span>🎮</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <strong>Hire Me, Please 🙃</strong>
              <p style="margin: 8px 0 0; color: var(--muted)">
                Internship or part-time frontend work would be awesome.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!--ABOUT-->
      <section id="about">
        <div class="about-wrapper">
          <div class="about-photo-big">
            <img src="/img/rere5.jpg" alt="Foto Reyna" />
          </div>

          <div class="about-right">
            <div class="about-tabs">
              <button class="tab active" data-target="tab1">Me in code</button>
              <button class="tab" data-target="tab2">Me in life</button>
            </div>

            <div class="about-card">
              <!-- Konten Tab 1 -->
              <div class="tab-content active" id="tab1">
                <h3>Behind the Screen. . .</h3>
                <p>
                  Seorang Fullstack Developer yang jatuh cinta pada dunia
                  frontend. Aku menikmati setiap proses membangun antarmuka —
                  mulai dari menerjemahkan desain, bermain dengan warna dan
                  tipografi, hingga menciptakan interaksi yang terasa alami.
                  Walau menguasai sisi backend dan logika sistem, bagiku yang
                  paling memuaskan adalah melihat hasil kerja langsung di layar
                  pengguna dan membuat mereka terhubung dengan produk yang
                  kubangun.
                </p>
                <p>
                  Buatku, frontend adalah ruang kreativitas. Di sanalah aku bisa
                  mengubah desain menjadi sesuatu yang interaktif, responsif,
                  dan menyenangkan digunakan. Aku suka memperhatikan detail —
                  dari transisi halus, layout yang rapi, hingga animasi kecil
                  yang bikin pengguna tersenyum. Setiap baris kode yang kutulis
                  bukan cuma soal fungsi, tapi juga soal menciptakan pengalaman.
                  Itulah mengapa, meski aku bisa fullstack, hatiku tetap milik
                  frontend. 🎨✨
                </p>
                <div class="about-mini">
                  <img src="/img/rere4.jpg" alt="Mini Foto Reyna" />
                  <span>#ReynaAydhina</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Konten Tab 2 -->
              <div class="tab-content" id="tab2">
                <h3>Not Just a Coder, Okay?</h3>
                <p>
                  Di luar ngoding, aku tuh orangnya cukup emosional — gampang
                  marah, gampang nangis, tapi juga gampang ketawa. Mood-ku
                  kadang naik turun kayak alur anime slice of life 😆 Tapi
                  justru dari situ aku belajar banyak hal tentang diri sendiri.
                  Aku suka banget hal-hal yang bisa bikin aku ngerasa “hidup”,
                  entah itu dari musik, film, atau anime yang bisa bikin aku
                  nangis tanpa alasan.
                </p>
                <p>
                  Kalau lagi nggak ngoding, aku biasanya main Roblox atau Mobile
                  Legends, sambil ngemil makanan manis (karena ya... aku dan
                  dessert tuh nggak bisa dipisahin 🍰). Dan tentu aja, aku punya
                  kucing lucu namanya Dodo 🐱 — partner setia yang selalu
                  nemenin aku, kayak sidekick di anime favoritku. Hidupku
                  mungkin sederhana, tapi selalu penuh warna dari hal-hal kecil
                  yang bikin bahagia. 🌸
                </p>
                <div class="about-mini">
                  <img src="/img/dodo.jpg" alt="Foto Character" />
                  <span>#Dodo</span>
                  <img src="/img/roblox-rere.jpg" alt="Foto Character" />
                  <span>#Roblox</span>
                  <img src="/img/arnold.jpeg" alt="Foto Character" />
                  <span>#Anime</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="about-tags">
              <span class="chip">#frontendlover</span>
              <span class="chip">#creativecode</span>
              <span class="chip">#roblox4ever</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="skills">
        <h2 class="section-title">Keahlian</h2>
        <div class="skills-categories">
          <div class="category-card">
            <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-code"></i></div>
            <h3>Frontend Core</h3>
            <p>Teknologi dasar untuk membangun UI modern</p>
            <div class="chips">
              <span class="chip"><i class="fa-brands fa-html5"></i> HTML</span>
              <span class="chip"
                ><i class="fa-brands fa-css3-alt"></i> CSS</span
              >
              <span class="chip"
                ><i class="fa-brands fa-js"></i> JavaScript</span
              >
              <span class="chip"><i class="fa-brands fa-react"></i> React</span>
              <span class="chip"><i class="fa-brands fa-php"></i> PHP</span>
              <span class="chip"
                ><i class="fa-brands fa-node-js"></i> Express.js</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="category-card">
            <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-toolbox"></i></div>
            <h3>Frameworks & Tools</h3>
            <p>Alat & framework untuk produktivitas developer</p>
            <div class="chips">
              <span class="chip"><i class="fa-solid fa-vial"></i> Postman</span>
              <span class="chip"
                ><i class="fa-solid fa-code-branch"></i> VS Code</span
              >
              <span class="chip"><i class="fa-brands fa-figma"></i> Figma</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="category-card">
            <div class="icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-group"></i></div>
            <h3>Soft Skills</h3>
            <p>Kemampuan pendukung untuk kerja tim yang solid</p>
            <div class="chips">
              <span class="chip"
                ><i class="fa-solid fa-people-arrows"></i> Teamwork</span
              >
              <span class="chip"
                ><i class="fa-solid fa-comments"></i> Komunikasi</span
              >
              <span class="chip"
                ><i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb"></i> Problem Solving</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- SKILLS -->
      <section>
        <div class="skills">
          <div class="skill" data-percent="90">
            <div class="skill-header">
              <i class="fa-brands fa-html5"></i>
              <h4>HTML/CSS</h4>
              <span class="percent">90%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bar"><span></span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="skill" data-percent="80">
            <div class="skill-header">
              <i class="fa-brands fa-js"></i>
              <h4>JavaScript</h4>
              <span class="percent">80%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bar"><span></span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="skill" data-percent="75">
            <div class="skill-header">
              <i class="fa-brands fa-react"></i>
              <h4>React</h4>
              <span class="percent">75%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bar"><span></span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="skill" data-percent="82">
            <div class="skill-header">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-palette"></i>
              <h4>UI/UX</h4>
              <span class="percent">82%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bar"><span></span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="skill" data-percent="78">
            <div class="skill-header">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-gauge-high"></i>
              <h4>Performance</h4>
              <span class="percent">78%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bar"><span></span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="skill" data-percent="85">
            <div class="skill-header">
              <i class="fa-brands fa-git-alt"></i>
              <h4>Git / Teamwork</h4>
              <span class="percent">85%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bar"><span></span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- PROJECT DESC -->
      <div class="portfolio-list">
        <div class="portfolio-item">
          <div class="thumb">
            <img src="/img/deskripsi-project/astra.png" alt="Thumbnail" />
          </div>
          <div class="info">
            <h3>ASTRA</h3>
            <p>
              Aplikasi pencatatan poin pelanggaran siswa/siswi SMKN 8 Malang
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="arrow">
            <a href="/pkl/astra">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="portfolio-item">
          <div class="thumb">
            <img src="/img/deskripsi-project/toko_online.png" alt="Thumbnail" />
          </div>
          <div class="info">
            <h3>Toko Online</h3>
            <p>Aplikasi E-commerce</p>
          </div>
          <div class="arrow">
            <a href="/pkl/toko_online">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="portfolio-item">
          <div class="thumb">
            <img
              src="/img/deskripsi-project/inventori_barang.png"
              alt="Thumbnail"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="info">
            <h3>Inventory Barang</h3>
            <p>Aplikasi CRUD sederhana</p>
          </div>
          <div class="arrow">
            <a href="/pkl/inventori_barang">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- PROJECT/PORTOFOLIO -->
      <section id="portfolio">
        <h2 class="section-title">
          Project Terbaru
          <i
            id="toggle-icon"
            class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"
            style="cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 8px"
          ></i>
        </h2>
        <div class="grid">
          <% projects.forEach((p, i)=> { %>
          <div class="project-card <%= i >= 3 ? 'hidden' : '' %>">
            <div class="thumb">
              <% if (p.thumbnail) { %>
              <img src="<%= p.thumbnail %>" alt="<%= p.title %>" />
              <% } else { %>
              <span class="placeholder">Mock Screenshot</span>
              <% } %>
            </div>

            <div class="info">
              <div class="title-row">
                <h3 class="title"><%= p.title %></h3>
                <% if (p.demo_url) { %>
                <div
                  class="icon"
                  onclick="window.open('<%= p.demo_url %>', '_blank')"
                >
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i>
                </div>
                <% } %>
              </div>

              <p class="desc"><%= p.description || "No description" %></p>
            </div>

            <div class="bottom">
              <% if (p.github_url) { %>
              <a href="<%= p.github_url %>" target="_blank" class="btn-icon"
                ><i class="fa-solid fa-file-code"></i
              ></a>
              <% } %> <% if (p.extra_url) { %>
              <a href="<%= p.extra_url %>" target="_blank" class="btn-icon"
                ><i class="fa-solid fa-link"></i
              ></a>
              <% } %> <% if (session && session.isLogin) { %>
              <div class="dropdown">
                <button class="btn-icon">
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-ellipsis-vertical"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="dropdown-menu">
                  <button
                    onclick="openEditModal('<%= p.id %>', '<%= p.title %>', `<%= p.description %>`, '<%= p.github_url %>', '<%= p.demo_url %>', '<%= p.extra_url %>')"
                  >
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-pen"></i> Edit
                  </button>
                  <button onclick="deleteProject('<%= p.id %>')">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-trash"></i> Hapus
                  </button>
                </div>
              </div>
              <% } %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% }) %>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Tombol trigger -->
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 16px">
        <% if (session && session.isLogin) { %>
        <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="openModal()">
          Tambah Project
        </button>
        <% } %>
      </div>

      <!-- Modal custom -->
      <div id="addProjectModal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <span class="close" onclick="closeModal()">&times;</span>
          <h2>Tambah Project</h2>
          <form
            action="/project/add"
            method="POST"
            enctype="multipart/form-data"
          >
            <label>Judul</label>
            <input type="text" name="title" required />

            <label>Deskripsi</label>
            <textarea name="description" rows="3"></textarea>

            <label>GitHub URL</label>
            <input type="text" name="github_url" />

            <label>Demo URL</label>
            <input type="text" name="demo_url" />

            <label>Extra URL</label>
            <input type="text" name="extra_url" />

            <label>Thumbnail</label>
            <input type="file" name="thumbnail" />

            <div class="actions">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Simpan</button>
              <button
                type="button"
                class="btn-secondary"
                onclick="closeModal()"
              >
                Batal
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Modal Add/Edit Project -->
      <div id="projectModal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <span class="close" onclick="closeModal()">&times;</span>
          <h2 id="modalTitle">Tambah Project</h2>
          <form
            id="projectForm"
            action="/project/add"
            method="POST"
            enctype="multipart/form-data"
          >
            <label>Judul</label>
            <input type="text" name="title" required />

            <label>Deskripsi</label>
            <textarea name="description" rows="4" required></textarea>

            <label>GitHub URL</label>
            <input type="text" name="github_url" />

            <label>Demo URL</label>
            <input type="text" name="demo_url" />

            <label>Extra URL</label>
            <input type="text" name="extra_url" />

            <label>Thumbnail</label>
            <input type="file" name="thumbnail" />

            <div class="actions">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Simpan</button>
              <button
                type="button"
                class="btn btn-secondary"
                onclick="closeModal()"
              >
                Batal
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CONTACT / FOOTER -->
      <section id="contact">
        <footer>
          <h2 class="section-title">Kontak</h2>
          <div class="contact">
            <div class="pill">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> reynaaydhina11@gmail.com
            </div>
            <div class="socials">
              <a href="https://www.instagram.com/aydhn_/" class="pill"
                ><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i> Instagram</a
              >
              <a href="https://github.com/Aydhina" class="pill"
                ><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i> GitHub</a
              >
              <a href="https://t.me/yooirere" class="pill"
                ><i class="fa-brands fa-telegram"></i> Telegram</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>© 2025 Reyna Aydhina Maritza. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
      </section>

      <!-- Modal Login -->
      <div id="loginModal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content" style="max-width: 400px">
          <span class="close" onclick="closeLoginModal()">&times;</span>
          <h2>Login</h2>
          <form id="loginForm" method="POST" action="/login">
            <label>Username</label>
            <input type="text" name="username" required />

            <label>Password</label>
            <input type="password" name="password" required />

            <div class="actions" style="margin-top: 12px">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%">
                Masuk
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <script src="/js/home.js"></script>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
